Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:03.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:07.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Lucy... You're actually a \Ndaughter of a really rich family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.22,0:00:09.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you ran away from home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:10.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:14.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you ate some super \Nfancy food, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:16.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're makin' me hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:18.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like fish from around the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that's where you were going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:28.67,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's love and dreams and you it'll become magical.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:35.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's cast a smile spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:48.77,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of admired this powerful world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:53.19,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,chock-full of problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:59.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Frozen time has started to move again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:05.58,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,ever since I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:11.00,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were we born? Why do we live?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:16.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any complicated answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:22.78,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Laugh! Cry! Be honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.78,0:01:27.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Simple feelings are the most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:35.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You can change those tears shed on sad nights into strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:42.53,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's cast a smile spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnolia in twilight...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:59.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is then that a single man arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:09.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are oddly quiet today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:12.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to have days \Nlike this once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:13.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of lonely, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:18.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... If only I had Virgo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:20.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have been able to dig it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:22.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still talking about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:26.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I could {\i1}so{\i0} care less about that \Nalready! Let's go on a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:28.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But {\i1}I{\i0} totally care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.45,0:02:33.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do about this month's rent?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:35.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go on a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:39.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a quick about-face, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:46.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally in the mood to work again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:49.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:53.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've always been working... \NJust here and there... Right, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:54.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:01.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:10.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Love & Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.23,0:03:17.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:21.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But lately I've been getting a \Nfeeling like I'm being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:23.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do they call that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:27.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called "being overly self-conscious"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:29.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that, sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:31.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it's just my imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:34.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two really do get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:35.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:39.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet up at noon tomorrow, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:42.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:42.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:56.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's... gonna be a fun... day of work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:03:59.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-chan, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:04.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I should wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:08.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful on your way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:09.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! Someone is watching me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:34.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's following me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:59.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:02.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:08.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:11.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:26.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:30.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:34.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And... what's with those clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:40.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heartfilia Railways was confiscated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:46.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost everything... My \Ncompany, my house, my money...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:48.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:53.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All the private property was \Nused as collateral, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:59.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this my reward for being a serious \Nbusinessman all these years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:04.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:06.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where mom's grave is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I transferred it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:19.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so much sad, as it is laughable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:24.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That much wealth, gone in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:30.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All my long years of achievement, \Nto naught in a single night...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:35.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The money I worked so hard for \NI even sacrificed my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:38.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's laughable! What a farce!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:50.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To see my daughter's face, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:53.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:57.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I told you not to lay \Na hand on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:02.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have that kind of power now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:07.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I only came to see how my daughter was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:11.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't give me that kind of look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:14.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about everything that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:17.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't plan to remain here long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:22.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go work at a \Ntrade guild in Acalypha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to start all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:27.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Acalypha?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see it soon if you \Ntravel to the west from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:32.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:35.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, about that, Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:38.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to need some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:45.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,100,000 jewel would be enough. \NWould you lend it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:48.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That much money? There's \Nno way I have that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:51.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just 100,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:55.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my daughter... I'm sure \Nyou have that much on hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:58.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you spouting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:02.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Money! And I'm putting my \Npride aside to beg you for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:03.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, even I!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:06.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! Now, give me money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:16.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:20.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how you treat your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:25.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you back then, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:33.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want isn't money, or pretty \Ndresses, or fortune forced upon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:38.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the same goes for you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:42.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any fortunes waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:43.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:43.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:09:00.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe him... How \Ncould he stoop so low?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:10.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Happy, is everything normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:12.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir! Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, there's no one suspicious around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:25.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:26.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:29.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This private here lacks enthusiasm, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I a private?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:33.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:35.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything okay, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:38.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:42.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! I've spotted a questionable subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:43.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:49.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was Gray that was following Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:54.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:55.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:59.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Lucy was being \Nfollowed by someone suspicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so I couldn't just leave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see how she was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:05.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He lllikes her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:07.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of running gag is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never really liked you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:11.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but you just dropped even \Nworse in my book, Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:17.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Going around topless is one \Nthing, but stalking girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:19.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Any way you look at it, you're a giant per...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:25.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I ain't gonna let you say it. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:27.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:30.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you crazy flame spewer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:33.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on, icy minty fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:37.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't fight in \Nfront of people's houses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:49.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, let's go on a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:51.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:55.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kind of job are we going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:56.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:00.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture the escaped convict Velveno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:04.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Velveno? You mean Velveno, the Guild Hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:06.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So they found out where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:09.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy uses some awesome magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:14.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The reward is 400,000 a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:16.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can pay your rent with that, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:20.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's about 6 \Nmonths' worth. I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:23.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear about \Nwhat's going on in Acalypha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:27.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some trade guild is being held \Nup by a group of armed robbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Acalypha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:37.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that armed group is actually \Nthe Dark Guild, Naked Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:42.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? Then the army ain't \Ngonna be able to handle them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:46.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, the number of Dark Guild \Nincidents has increased a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:48.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:53.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go work at a \Ntrade guild in Acalypha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:55.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.96,0:12:06.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what happens \Nto him... It's not my...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:10.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Acalypha?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:14.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:18.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not here. I wonder where she went?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:19.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:27.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he is that man... I have to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:41.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The trade guild Love & Lucky \Nin the town of Acalypha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:46.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened to the hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:49.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save them! My husband is in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:55.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've put up requests for assistance \Nat nearby wizard guilds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:57.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous, so stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:12:59.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:03.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:07.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now... Civilians can't go inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:09.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I might have family in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:10.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:23.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! No means no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:28.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to do something... Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:32.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Maiden, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:37.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Virgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, is it time for punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:45.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:46.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a favor to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:54.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:14:00.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I am able to \Nenter into the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Virgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:02.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You wish to punish me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:04.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thanking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:07.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are a number of wizards inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:10.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will we be okay with just ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:11.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:13.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:30.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I thought a trade guild would \Nhave a ton of cash, but this is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:33.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We should have just gone for a bank instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:38.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't got no time! Hurry and \Nput the money in the sacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:43.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuddap, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:48.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? "Mmph, mmph, mmph?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:50.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your butt itches or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:58.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't get this money, \Nwe're in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:00.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:03.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't got no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:09.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Taurus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:13.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow you to lay hands on a lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:14.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:15.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A cow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:16.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's a Spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is a Spirit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd it come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.43,0:15:24.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's far enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:25.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:26.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:28.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a wizard from an \Nofficial guild! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:31.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be good, or you're gonna get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:38.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's scissors are sharper than ever-ebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sagittarius!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:46.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will bring them all down, \Nas it were. Moshimoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:51.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The final blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:54.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what magic she'll use next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:56.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:58.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:11.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappointing-ebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Break in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:20.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it when I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:22.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:30.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:32.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your magic's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:34.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We also wish to give you our thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:37.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:39.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:42.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a wizard from Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:47.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so shocked such an incredible \Nperson came to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:00.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:06.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So... Is he safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:07.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:10.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:21.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...you just came to town?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:25.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any money, so \NI walked all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:27.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So all that was for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:30.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait... You wanted to borrow \N100,000 for traveling money?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:33.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of warped sense \Nof prices do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:36.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:41.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because I heard that the guild \Nyou were headed to was attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:45.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, a number have escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:50.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You came here worried for your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:53.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As if! I'm outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:57.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:17:59.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get any strange ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:07.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I've forgiven you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:10.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:12.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:19.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have traveled quite a long way, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:22.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've also had a lot of time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:26.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:27.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't thinking straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:32.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I regret what I did. It's shameful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:35.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to change who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:38.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without money, I made it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:41.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:51.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guild is the place I met \NLayla... I mean, your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:56.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was thinking about going independent,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:59.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that was right when you were \Nin your mother's stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:03.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us quit the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:07.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But right then, the guild's signboard broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:10.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky turned into Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:13.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite a strange thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.49,0:19:19.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us decided that if we \Nhad a daughter to name her Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:27.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:32.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't decide your daughter's \Nname on a whim like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:37.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:40.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad I got to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:45.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as Lucky Lucy of the Heartfilias...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:51.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to see you as "Just \NLucy", like you wanted to become.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:19:59.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, you safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:01.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:03.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:09.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be you handled \Neverything here yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:12.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:20.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay well, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:27.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was with you all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:28.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:30.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing my butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:33.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We canceled the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:34.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:44.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really such a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:57.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The main headquarters of \Nthe Dark Guild Naked Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:03.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:05.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sworry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:08.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An official guild got in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:11.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't get our hands on anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:15.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:19.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:23.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You said the same line twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:27.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If they ain't got it, they \Nain't got it, Gato-niisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:31.29,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,-niisan is an honorific for one's older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:31.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a time to be \Nlaughing, Zato-niisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:35.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming close to the deadline \Nfor paying our dues to Oración Seis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:39.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a time to be \Nlaughing, Zato-niisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.89,0:21:42.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You repeated yourself again, Gato-niisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:46.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wondered, but how can \Nthey both be the older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:52.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There ain't any Dark Guilds \Nthat disobeys Oración Seis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:53.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There ain't any Dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:55.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you the first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:59.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bastards suddenly upped \Nthe money payments they demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:22:02.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are they plannin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:10.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.38,0:22:15.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the changing of an \Nera... The sound of eyes opening...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.99,0:22:17.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of something beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.89,0:22:20.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The breaking of the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.07,0:23:58.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, the master was calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.78,0:24:01.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wanted to talk\Nabout some important job.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.82,0:24:03.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there was some big crisis...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.84,0:24:09.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like we're going to team up with \Nsome other guilds to go defeat a Dark Guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.80,0:24:12.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't sound like your everyday gig!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.23,0:24:13.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gettin' fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.90,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Allied Forces, Gather Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:18.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of people will gather up?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.73,0:24:22.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fateful encounter! That's \Nromance! That's suspense!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.88,0:24:23.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.89,0:24:26.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
